  "title": "6 Months Bank Officer (Corporate Actions)  #NJN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Tampines till May 26 then shift to Raffles</strong></p><p><strong>\nResponsibilities </strong></p><p>·          Timely and accurate data entry for processing of all Incomes/Corporate events (Inputter/Checker). </p><p>·          Liaise with custodians for clarification on incomes/events. </p><p>·          Prepare disclosure letter of shareholder request from companies. </p><p>·          Handle queries from RMs/MAs/Custodians on the incomes/events. </p><p>·          Pass entries for commission fees collected or update waiver file if fees are waived.</p><p>·          Participate in UAT and ad hoc projects </p><p><br />Jessica Nguyen Huynh Thanh Truc</p><p>CEI Reg. No. R23113787</p><p>EA License No. 99C4599</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p></p>",
